<T>__{smash cut to:}
<L>__{interior texas state pen, 1998 infirmary entrance day}
<A>__{phillip flails as guards hold him back from a doctor.}
<C>__{phillip}
<D>__{let me in! just let me in!}
<C>__{doctor}
<D>__{he's not here!}
<C>__{phillip}
<D>__{i need to see him!}
<C>__{doctor}
<D>__{i told you he's not here! you need to calm down.}
<A>__{phillip calms himself.}
<C>__{phillip}
<D>__{just tell me where he is. what happened?}
<C>__{doctor}
<D>__{he slipped into a coma for a few days. he's conscious now, but he's very sick. we had him transferred to a private care facility. there was nothing we could do for him here. it's just a matter of time now.}
